</div> 
</nav> 
<div id="toast" class="toast"></div> 
<!-- HOME --> 
<div class="page active" id="pg-home"> 
<div class="hero"> 
<div class="hbg"></div><div class="hgrid"></div> 
<div style="max-width:620px;position:relative"> 
<div class="htag">Live GPS Tracking</div> 
<h1>Move Goods.<br><em>Faster.</em> Smarter.<br>Anywhere.</h1> 
<p>SwiftHaul connects businesses to a reliable fleet for road, air and sea freight — with real-time 
tracking at every step.</p> 
<div class="hctas"> 
<button class="btn btn-p" onclick="go('signup')">Get Started Free</button> 
<button class="btn btn-o" onclick="go('track')">Track Shipment</button> 
</div> 
<div class="hstats"> 
<div><div class="snum">12K+</div><div class="slbl">Deliveries/Month</div></div> 
<div><div class="snum">98.4%</div><div class="slbl">On-Time Rate</div></div> 
<div><div class="snum">47</div><div class="slbl">Countries Served</div></div> 
</div> 
</div> 
</div> 
<div class="sec"> 
<div class="htag" style="margin-bottom:.9rem">Our Services</div> 
<div class="stitle">Shipping Solutions for Every Need</div> 
<div class="ssub">From last-mile delivery to international freight at honest prices.</div> 
<div class="grid3"> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(249,115,22,.15)">           
</div><h3>Road Freight</h3><p>FTL &amp; LTL 
across India. GPS-tracked, insured, door-to-door.</p><div class="cprice">₹8 <small>/ km · per 
tonne</small></div></div> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(59,130,246,.15)">    
</div><h3>Air Cargo</h3><p>Next-day domestic, 2
5 day international express air freight.</p><div class="cprice">₹180 <small>/ kg 
domestic</small></div></div> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(34,197,94,.15)">             
</div><h3>Sea Freight</h3><p>FCL &amp; LCL 
ocean freight for bulk international shipments.</p><div class="cprice">₹2,400 <small>/ CBM · 
FCL</small></div></div> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(168,85,247,.15)">      
</div><h3>Express Parcel</h3><p>Same-day &amp; 
next-day parcel delivery for e-commerce &amp; docs.</p><div class="cprice">₹45 <small>/ parcel 
&lt;5 kg</small></div></div> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(236,72,153,.15)"> 
</div><h3>Cold Chain</h3><p>Reefer logistics for 
pharma &amp; food. –20°C to +25°C range.</p><div class="cprice">₹22 <small>/ km 
reefer</small></div></div> 
<div class="card"><div class="cicon" 
style="background:rgba(234,179,8,.15)">             
</div><h3>Warehousing</h3><p>14 distribution 
centers across India, short &amp; long term.</p><div class="cprice">₹12 <small>/ sq.ft / 
month</small></div></div> 
</div> 
</div> 
<div style="background:var(--s1);border-radius:20px;margin:0 2rem;padding:3rem 2.5rem"> 
<div class="stitle">How It Works</div> 
<div class="ssub">Shipping with SwiftHaul takes under 3 minutes to set up.</div> 
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:1.8rem"> 
<div style="text-align:center"><div style="width:50px;height:50px;border
radius:12px;background:rgba(249,115,22,.12);border:1px solid 
rgba(249,115,22,.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;margin:0 
auto .9rem">         
</div><h4 style="font-family:var(--fh);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">1. 
Book Online</h4><p style="color:var(--mu);font-size:13px">Enter details, get instant 
quote.</p></div> 
<div style="text-align:center"><div style="width:50px;height:50px;border
radius:12px;background:rgba(59,130,246,.12);border:1px solid 
rgba(59,130,246,.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;margin:0 
auto .9rem">       
</div><h4 style="font-family:var(--fh);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">2. We 
Pick Up</h4><p style="color:var(--mu);font-size:13px">Driver arrives in your window.</p></div> 
<div style="text-align:center"><div style="width:50px;height:50px;border
radius:12px;background:rgba(168,85,247,.12);border:1px solid 
rgba(168,85,247,.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;margin:0 
auto .9rem">   
</div><h4 style="font-family:var(--fh);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">3. 
Track Live</h4><p style="color:var(--mu);font-size:13px">Real-time GPS from pickup to 
drop.</p></div> 
<div style="text-align:center"><div style="width:50px;height:50px;border
radius:12px;background:rgba(34,197,94,.12);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.25);display:flex;align
items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;margin:0 auto .9rem">  
</div><h4 style="font
family:var(--fh);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">4. Delivered</h4><p style="color:var(-
mu);font-size:13px">Proof of delivery sent instantly.</p></div> 
</div> 
</div> 
<div style="height:3rem"></div> 
</div> 
<!-- TRACK --> 
<div class="page" id="pg-track"> 
<div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:2.5rem 2rem"> 
<div class="stitle">Track Your Shipment</div> 
<p style="color:var(--mu);margin-bottom:1.8rem;font-size:14px">Enter your tracking ID for real
time location and status updates.</p> 
<div class="fbox"> 
<div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap"> 
<div style="flex:1;min-width:200px"><label>Tracking ID</label><input id="tid" 
placeholder="e.g. SH-48291" oninput="this.value=this.value.toUpperCase()"></div> 
<div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end"><button class="btn btn-p" onclick="doTrack()" 
style="height:40px">Track Now</button></div> 
</div> 
<p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mu);margin-top:9px">Try: <a onclick="quickTrack('SH
48291')" style="color:var(--ac);cursor:pointer">SH-48291</a> · <a onclick="quickTrack('SH
77312')" style="color:var(--ac);cursor:pointer">SH-77312</a> · <a onclick="quickTrack('SH
10045')" style="color:var(--ac);cursor:pointer">SH-10045</a></p> 
</div> 
<div id="track-res" style="display:none"> 
<div class="fbox"> 
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;flex
wrap:wrap;gap:.8rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem"> 
<div><p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mu);margin-bottom:3px">TRACKING ID</p><h3 
